لرَّحْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two sides &c. of the camel's saddle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And in like manner, (M,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafA_ataA AlmuSoHafi","text_ar":"دَفاـَتَا المُصْحَفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The two sides"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"boards"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the book;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two things that embrace the book between them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, Mgh, K, * TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two faces, that are on the two sides, of the book."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafiZa maA bayona Ald~af~atayoni","text_ar":"حَفِظَ مَا بَيْنَ الدَّفَّتَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He retained in his memory,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"got by heart, what is between the two boards,"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the whole contents,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the book]. (TA.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daf~apN","text_ar":"دَفَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A board"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a general sense; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daf~N","text_ar":"دَفٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". And hence, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rudder."},{"kind":"text","text":"] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daf~apu AlT~aboli","text_ar":"دَفَّةُ الطَّبْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of skin"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is upon the head of the drum:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in a copy of the M:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daf~ataA AlT~aboli","text_ar":"دَفَّتَا الطَّبْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two things,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two pieces of skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are upon the head"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the two extremities"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"common cylindrical"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drum."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba daf~atiY AlT~aboli","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ دَفَّتِى الطَّبْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He beat the two skins of the drum"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","T","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}